<br>
Personally, I'm at 33 points and I went for spell casting mastery level 3, innate ivu, dire charm, and undead mez.  <br>
<br>
I've heard some STRANGE things, like necromancers getting MENTAL CLARITY first.  (you know who you are, but I still love ya for it)<br>
<br>
My next skill will likely be fearstorm, or perhaps I'll save up for lifeburn.  That would get me the lich title a few days sooner, and thats not a bad thing. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->    I SHOULD get the summon corpse skill though.<br>
<br>
